/write field access), which points to incomplete test reachability metadata for the `ByteBufferWriter` path. Dynamic-access coverage is unavailable for this run.\n\nPlease inspect:\n- `human-intervention-logs/com.typesafe.akka:akka-protobuf-v3_2.13:2.8.8/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-04T14-04-13-514138Z.log`\n- `human-intervention-logs/com.typesafe.akka:akka-protobuf-v3_2.13:2.8.8/fix-java-run-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-04T14-06-45-341865Z.log`\n- `human-intervention-logs/com.typesafe.akka:akka-protobuf-v3_2.13:2.8.8/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-04T14-08-08-158729Z.log`\n- `human-intervention-logs/com.typesafe.akka:akka-protobuf-v3_2.13:2.8.8/native-test-verify/cycle-1-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-04T14-08-43-723692Z.log`\n- `stats/com.typesafe.akka/akka-protobuf-v3_2.13/2.8.8/execution-metrics.json`\n\nNext steps:\n1. Update `tests/src/com.typesafe.akka/akka-protobuf-v3_2.13/2.8.8/src/test/scala/com_typesafe_akka/akka_protobuf_v3_2_13/MessageSchemaTest.scala` to assert `ExceptionInInitializerError` and validate its `RuntimeException` cause.\n2. Re-run `./gradlew javaTest -Pcoordinates=com.typesafe.akka:akka-protobuf-v3_2.13:2.8.8`, then add the missing reflection metadata for `java.io.FileOutputStream.channel` needed by `ByteBufferWriterTest`.\n3. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=com.typesafe.akka:akka-protobuf-v3_2.13:2.8.8` and refresh stats once both the Java and native paths pass."}}
